{"tid":192632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線有片]血洗ATM兩死！劫匪狂捅無辜男10刀再殺人","createTime":"2017-04-08T17:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T01:02:42.000Z","uid":54733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"399301cbb707562e76073bf534ec175f2556ffd8","tid":192632,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170408/large/1491664326_7275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F1491664326_7275.jpg&h=48253c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東汕頭市的中國工商銀行，今日傍晚6時36分許發生一宗懷疑搶劫傷人案，事件造成兩人死亡，網傳兇徒今晚已落網。根據監控鏡頭顯示，一名撓手男子疑用報紙收藏利刀扮等撳錢，等待時機成熟，就施施然打開包着執紙的藏刀，捅向身邊穿着格子恤衫的男子。現場留下滿地鮮血，而被捅了10刀的男子負傷離開現場。<br />\n<br />\n至於，留在ATM櫃員機操作的另一名白衣男子，看到這驚嚇一幕時，不知所措，持刀男子則用刀指嚇他，他才驚覺立即逃跑。持刀男子在櫃員機取款後，即匆匆逃去。<br />\n<br />\n網上有消息指，在該路段附近之後再發生持刀傷人，疑似同一男子再殺途人，另一條網上流傳片段則看到，一名男子滿身鮮血倒臥在路邊，醫生到場為其急救。峽山派出所在官方微博作出緊急通知，今晚6時許到7時，在中國工商銀行附近、洋汾林桂林路段發生1宗持刀傷人案件，要求當值警員加緊巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56539745&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56539745%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170408&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=004ec028\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56539745%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170408&h=d7beb36b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56539745&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170408</a>"},{"pid":"f8b80c34213a546229ff0d55478bcacfacbc9068","tid":192632,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"跟係謀殺"},{"pid":"0962e3925f42a6a3903da166b6da6433cc